---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BreakingNews from '../components/BreakingNews.astro';

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<Layout title="Alpe Pianello - A Community in Progress">
  <Hero 
    title="Welcome to Alpe Pianello"
    subtitle="A community in progress where exploration and growth meet daily life."
    contactName="Adam"
  />
  
  <section class="letter-section">
    <div class="letter-content">
      <h2>A Letter from Us to You</h2>
      
      <div class="letter">
        <p>Living in community is a dream—and, at times, a paradox. It's a vision of something better: a life where work, play, and rest are woven together in harmony, where the effort we give sustains not just the place but the people within it.</p>
        
        <p>We're not offering perfection—far from it. What we're offering is an experiment, a wild and meaningful attempt to create a life where the foundations of sustainability support the freedom to explore, connect, and grow.</p>
        
        <p>Come share your experience with others. Come see what it's like to dream together and build something real. Come, as you are, to this space where you can belong and help us imagine what's possible.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <BreakingNews />
</Layout>

<style>
  .letter-section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background-color: #fff;
    background-image: url('/Wood.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    position: relative;
  }

  .letter-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  .letter-content {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #2d3436;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .letter {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .letter p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #2d3436;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .letter-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .letter {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .letter p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>